---

<!-- Supply Chain AI Deep Dive Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-blue-900/10 dark:to-cyan-900/10">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-cyan-100 dark:from-blue-900/30 dark:to-cyan-900/30 rounded-full mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></span>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">SUPPLY CHAIN AI</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-[1.1]">
          How AI Solves Complex Supply Chain Problems
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Supply chain disruptions cost enterprises millions annually.</span> Our team brings 14+ years of hands-on experience in foodservice and logistics operations, combining deep industry expertise with cutting-edge AI solutions.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-cyan-900/20 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-200/50 dark:border-blue-700/30">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Real-World Experience</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Our senior consultant has spent over 14 years as a Director of Client Solutions, specializing in supply chain technology, engineering, and financial management. This hands-on experience in creating smaller, smarter, and more agile supply chains is now enhanced with AI-powered insights.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">1</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Predictive Demand Intelligence</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">AI models analyze historical patterns, seasonal trends, and external market factors to predict demand with 85-95% accuracy. This eliminates the guesswork that leads to overstock and stockouts, reducing inventory carrying costs by 25-30%.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">2</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Intelligent Supplier Risk Management</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Real-time monitoring of supplier performance, financial health, and geopolitical risks. AI algorithms identify potential disruptions weeks before they impact operations, enabling proactive sourcing decisions and alternative supplier activation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">3</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Dynamic Logistics Optimization</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Machine learning algorithms continuously optimize routing, warehouse allocation, and transportation modes. This results in 15-20% reduction in logistics costs while improving delivery times and customer satisfaction scores.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- HilBar-Style Metrics Dashboard -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-200/50 dark:border-slate-600/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-center">Supply Chain AI Impact Metrics</h3>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-600 mb-2">30%</div>
